import React from 'react'
import { AppBar, Box, Toolbar, Typography } from '@mui/material'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Box>
      <AppBar className='!bg-black shadow-xl !shadow-slate-900'>
        <Toolbar>
          <Typography className='!font-bold'>Grocery Shop</Typography>
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>
    </Box>
    </>
  )
}

export default Header
